                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d252">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Snyder</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-07-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 11, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Snyder reports that a decree has been issued by the Government of Colombia
                    prohibiting the receipt in custom-houses of <hi rend="italic">vales
                        extranjeros</hi>, which practically annuls the claims of citizens of the
                    United States.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
